* Dada Upasana :
2 times Aanik
3 times Hanuman Chalisa
1 time Aniruddha Chalisa
5 times Dattabavani
5 times Shubhankara Stotra
5 times Ashubnashini Stotra
Gurucharitra 18 Aadhay
Gurucharitra 14 Aadhay
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Nandai Upasana :
1 Aadhay Matruvatsalya
1 Aadhay Upanishad
1 Bapu Grantha atleast 1 Page
All Prarthana Matruvatsalya and Upanishad
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Bapu :
1 Ramraksha
5 times Gurumantra
11 or 5 times Panchamukh kavach
10 minutes Dhyan
Darshan Upsana
16 Mala
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Extra Upsana :
Ghorkasta Stotra
Dattamala Mantra
Hanuman Stotra
Sunderkand
Aniruddha Kavach
Om manasamarthya data jaap
Nandai Upasana
Suchit dada Jap
